1
00:00:00,120 --> 00:00:05,200
Let me tell you a secret: the charts 
look different to professional traders! 

2
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:07,400
That’s because they see the “manipulation”  

3
00:00:07,400 --> 00:00:09,444
candles that you don't!
These candles are the key  

4
00:00:09,444 --> 00:00:11,560
